name: chenille burp cloth set
description:
So, so cute! These burp cloths are just so sweet! The cowboy print has that vintage look that is just so popular now.  The chenille is a cream color and matches the print just perfect. Fits great on your shoulder or lap. Would make a great emergency changing pad will you were out and needed somewhere clean to lay your baby. 

Approximate size is 9 inches x 16 inches. 
Set of 2.

name: Live Well Kitchen Towel
description:
A great reminder for any kitchen. "Live well, Laugh often, Love much"  White microfiber towel measures 16inches by 26 inches. 
Machine washable.

name: chenille bib and burp cloth set
description:
Super soft and sweet! This cream chenille bib and burp cloth set features 1 chenille bib with polka dots on the reverse & velcro closure and 2 chenille burp cloths(polka dots and stripes).  Orange, blue and brown stripes/dots. 

Perfect for a sweet little boy. Our burp cloths are the perfect size for your shoulder or lap. They even make a great emergency changing pad. :o)
